results.title: Facing Facts
results.description: Young Tony goes to jail, and is bailed out by Kris.  A Japanese Firm buys out Stark Enterprises.

results.title: Good as Gone
results.description: War Machine introduces young Stark to his heritage.

results.title: Going for Broke
results.description: Iron Man and War Machine battle Stockpile and the old versions of the Iron Man armor.
